item.title: Ok guys i need help for the game now
item.dc:creator: @mstcool_2 mstcool 2
item.description:
@mstcool_2 wrote:

tann:

Lol, this guy is saying that when he tries to portforward his ports he types in “192.168.1._” in his URL box and it takes him to a website instead of his Router login box, I’m guessing that’s what he is talking about. and if you’re trying to run a hamachi server download a source, run it, download a client compatiable with the source, change the ip inside that client to your hamachi id, look up tutorials if you don’t know how. then advertise your server on hamachi sites… have fun hosting.
